y 'I don't mind telling you' to emphasize the statement you are making.\nI don't mind telling you I was absolutely terrified.", '(用于强调将要说的话)我不介意告诉你\n说真的，我当时吓坏了。'], ["PHRASE\nIf you say that you wouldn't mind something, you mean that you would quite like it.\nI wouldn't mind a coffee...\nAnne wouldn't mind going to Italy or France to live.", '很喜欢;很愿意\n我很愿意喝杯咖啡。\n安妮很愿意去意大利或法国定居。']]}]